{"items":[{"term":"薄縭絲","pronunciation":"po̍h-li-si","definition":"形容東西厚度很薄或是分量很少。","fieldNote":"清晨出門，阿嬤在廚房聽到開門聲，探頭看了我一眼。我穿著一件薄汗衫。她說「穿甲薄縭絲」，聲音不大，比較像說給自己聽的。我說「沒關係啦」就走了。到了巷口，風吹過來，真的有點涼。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/12340/","imageAlt":"薄縭絲","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/32e6e28b4705224a-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/32e6e28b4705224a-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/32e6e28b4705224a-480.webp 480w, assets/images/32e6e28b4705224a-768.webp 768w, assets/images/32e6e28b4705224a-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/32e6e28b4705224a-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"凊彩","pronunciation":"tshìn-tshái","definition":"副詞，隨便、馬馬虎虎；形容詞，任何；形容詞，隨和、不謹慎。","fieldNote":"外婆炒菜從不量，鹽巴抓一把，醬油沿鍋邊淋一圈，蒜頭用刀背拍扁直接丟進去。我問她放多少，她頭也不抬，說「凊彩仔啦，有啥放啥」，鍋鏟繼續鏟。我站在灶邊，油蒜的味道一陣一陣竄過來，什麼比例都記不起來。但那個菜，我現在還記得味道。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/5755/","imageAlt":"凊彩","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/a3c7294c6db3e4e6-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/a3c7294c6db3e4e6-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/a3c7294c6db3e4e6-480.webp 480w, assets/images/a3c7294c6db3e4e6-768.webp 768w, assets/images/a3c7294c6db3e4e6-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/a3c7294c6db3e4e6-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"日花","pronunciation":"ji̍t-hue","definition":"陽光穿過雲間或葉縫,在地面、水面、牆上形成碎花般閃爍的光影。","fieldNote":"阿公的藤椅上,一塊一塊的光在動。是樹葉在風裡晃,光就跟著晃。小時候我以為那是螢火蟲在白天出來偷跑。後來知道,這個叫日花。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/1171/","imageAlt":"日花","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/f1ca8d9fd262e140-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/f1ca8d9fd262e140-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/f1ca8d9fd262e140-480.webp 480w, assets/images/f1ca8d9fd262e140-768.webp 768w, assets/images/f1ca8d9fd262e140-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/f1ca8d9fd262e140-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}}]}
